vernac_cmds: Inductive match_fdecs: list (ident * fundef) -> funspecs -> Prop := | match_fdecs_nil: match_fdecs nil nil | match_fdecs_cons: forall i fd fspec fs G, type_of_fundef fd = type_of_funspec fspec -> match_fdecs fs G -> match_fdecs ((i,fd)::fs) ((i,fspec)::G) .
Lemma match_fdecs_exists_Gfun: forall prog G i f, find_id i G = Some f -> match_fdecs (prog_funct prog) G -> exists fd, In (i, Gfun fd) (prog_defs prog) /\ type_of_fundef fd = type_of_funspec f.
revert G; induction dl; simpl; intros.
simpl in H; if_tac in H.

Lemma initial_core_ok: forall (prog: program) G n m, list_norepet (prog_defs_names prog) -> match_fdecs (prog_funct prog) G -> Genv.init_mem prog = Some m -> initial_rmap_ok m (initial_core (Genv.globalenv prog) G n).
case_eq (@Genv.invert_symbol (Ctypes.fundef function) type (@Genv.globalenv (Ctypes.fundef function) type prog) b); intros; try now (rewrite core_NO; auto).
case_eq (find_id i G); intros; [ | rewrite core_NO; auto].
change (AST.prog_defs prog) with (prog_defs prog) in H.
revert dl H H5 H1; induction n; simpl; intros.
apply (in_map (@fst ident (globdef fundef type))) in H.
apply (in_map (@fst ident (globdef fundef type))) in H2.
clear - RANGE H2 H1 H Hm.
change (AST.prog_defs prog) with (prog_defs prog) in Hm.
replace (length (rev dl) - nat_of_Z (Z.pos b - 1) - 1)%nat with (length (rev dl) - nat_of_Z (Z.pos b))%nat in H5.
clear RANGE; rename H0 into RANGE.
forget (rev dl) as dl'; clear dl; rename dl' into dl.
revert m Hm H1 H5; induction dl; intros.
inversion H5; clear H5; subst a.
replace (length (a::dl) - Pos.to_nat b)%nat with (S (length dl - Pos.to_nat b))%nat in H5.

Definition initial_jm (prog: program) m (G: funspecs) (n: nat) (H: Genv.init_mem prog = Some m) (H1: list_norepet (prog_defs_names prog)) (H2: match_fdecs (prog_funct prog) G) : juicy_mem := initial_mem m (initial_core (Genv.globalenv prog) G n) (initial_core_ok _ _ _ m H1 H2 H).

Lemma initial_jm_age (prog: program) m (G: funspecs) (n : nat) (H: Genv.init_mem prog = Some m) (H1: list_norepet (prog_defs_names prog)) (H2: match_fdecs (prog_funct prog) G) : age (initial_mem m (initial_core (Genv.globalenv prog) G (S n)) (initial_core_ok _ _ _ m H1 H2 H)) (initial_mem m (initial_core (Genv.globalenv prog) G n ) (initial_core_ok _ _ _ m H1 H2 H)).
match goal with |- context [ proj1_sig ?x ] => destruct x as (r & lev & bah & Hg1); simpl end.
match goal with |- context [ proj1_sig ?x ] => destruct x as (r' & lev' & bah' & Hg2); simpl end.
destruct p; unfold resource_fmap; f_equal; try apply preds_fmap_NoneP.
match goal with | |- ?A (?B ?C) = _ => change (A (B C)) with ((A oo B) C) end.

Definition initial_jm_ext {Z} (ora : Z) (prog: program) m (G: funspecs) (n: nat) (H: Genv.init_mem prog = Some m) (H1: list_norepet (prog_defs_names prog)) (H2: match_fdecs (prog_funct prog) G) : juicy_mem := initial_mem m (initial_core_ext ora (Genv.globalenv prog) G n) (initial_core_ext_ok _ _ _ _ m H1 H2 H).

Lemma initial_jm_ext_eq : forall {Z} (ora : Z) (prog: program) m (G: funspecs) (n: nat) (H: Genv.init_mem prog = Some m) (H1: list_norepet (prog_defs_names prog)) (H2: match_fdecs (prog_funct prog) G), join (m_phi (initial_jm prog m G n H H1 H2)) (set_ghost (core (m_phi (initial_jm prog m G n H H1 H2))) (Some (ext_ghost ora, NoneP) :: nil) eq_refl) (m_phi (initial_jm_ext ora prog m G n H H1 H2)).
Lemma initial_jm_without_locks prog m G n H H1 H2: no_locks (m_phi (initial_jm prog m G n H H1 H2)).
match goal with |- context [ proj1_sig ?a ] => destruct a as (phi & lev & E & ?) end; simpl.
destruct (fst ((snd (unsquash (initial_core (Genv.globalenv prog) G n)))) addr); congruence.
Lemma initial_jm_ext_without_locks {Z} (ora : Z) prog m G n H H1 H2: no_locks (m_phi (initial_jm_ext ora prog m G n H H1 H2)).
match goal with |- context [ proj1_sig ?a ] => destruct a as (phi & lev & E & ?) end; simpl.
destruct (fst ((snd (unsquash (initial_core_ext ora (Genv.globalenv prog) G n)))) addr); congruence.

Definition matchfunspecs (ge : genv) (G : funspecs) (Phi : rmap) : Prop := forall (b : block) fsig cc A P Q, func_at'' fsig cc A P Q (b, 0%Z) Phi -> exists id P' Q' P'_ne Q'_ne, Genv.find_symbol ge id = Some b /\ find_id id G = Some (mk_funspec fsig cc A P' Q' P'_ne Q'_ne) /\ cond_approx_eq (level Phi) A P P' /\ cond_approx_eq (level Phi) A Q Q'.
Lemma initial_jm_matchfunspecs prog m G n H H1 H2: matchfunspecs (globalenv prog) G (m_phi (initial_jm prog m G n H H1 H2)).
match goal with |- context [ proj1_sig ?a ] => destruct a as (phi & lev & E & ?) end; simpl.
intros b fsig cc A P Q FAT.
assert (Pi : initial_core (Genv.globalenv prog) G n @ (b, 0) = PURE (FUN fsig cc) (preds_fmap (approx n) (approx n) pp)).
destruct (access_at m (b, 0)) as [[]|]; simpl in E2; try congruence.
destruct (fst ( (snd (unsquash (initial_core (Genv.globalenv prog) G n)))) (b, 0)) as [t | t p k p0 | k p] eqn:E'''; simpl in E2; try congruence.
destruct f0 as [f1 c0 A0 P0 Q0 P_ne0 Q_ne0].
exists i, P0, Q0, P_ne0, Q_ne0.
all: apply equal_f_dep with (x := ts) in EE.
all: apply equal_f_dep with (x := a) in EE.
1: apply equal_f_dep with (x := true) in EE.
2: apply equal_f_dep with (x := false) in EE.
all: apply equal_f_dep with (x := ge) in EE.

match goal with |- context [ proj1_sig ?a ] => destruct a as (phi & lev & E & ?) end; simpl.
intros b fsig cc A P Q FAT.

destruct (access_at m (b, 0)) as [[]|]; simpl in E2; try congruence.
destruct (fst ( (snd (unsquash (initial_core_ext ora (Genv.globalenv prog) G n)))) (b, 0)) as [t | t p k p0 | k p] eqn:E'''; simpl in E2; try congruence.
destruct f0 as [f1 c0 A0 P0 Q0 P_ne0 Q_ne0].
exists i, P0, Q0, P_ne0, Q_ne0.
all: apply equal_f_dep with (x := ts) in EE.
all: apply equal_f_dep with (x := a) in EE.
1: apply equal_f_dep with (x := true) in EE.
2: apply equal_f_dep with (x := false) in EE.
all: apply equal_f_dep with (x := ge) in EE.
